Big Brother Naija Season 4 has finally come to an end with it recording its first female winner, Mercy. It was 3 months of steady drama as it was tagged “Pepper Dem”; different housemates came with different tactics. After weeks of voting and evictions, it came down to the final 5 – Omashola, Frodd, Seyi, Mike and Mercy. But, as we now know Mercy was the most voted for out of the 5, hence her winning the prize. Read More: Mercy Lambo Wins BBNaija Season 4 Fans of the reality TV show and winner, Mercy have taken to social media to react to the announcement:        